This soup is nicknamed “jewel of the South-East” because it is one of the most expensive soups in Igboland. Ever heard of the saying, “better soup, na money kill am”? Well, Ofe Owerri is that soup and here’s how to prepare the soup of kings. Ingredients Instructions Your Ofe Owerri is ready! Serve with any ‘swallow’ of your choice. www.pulse.ng